*OutputBin Bin5/Finisher Shift Tray: "
 <</OutputType (Finisher Shift Tray) >> setpagedevice"
*End
*OutputBin BookletFinisherStack/Booklet Finisher Tray: "
 <</OutputType (Booklet Finisher Stack)>> setpagedevice"
