 /Policies <</MediaType 2>> >> setpagedevice"
*End
*MediaType RECYCLED/Recycled: "<</MediaType (Recycled)
 /Policies <</MediaType 2>> >> setpagedevice"
*End
*MediaType SPECIAL/Special: "<</MediaType (Special)
 /Policies <</MediaType 2>> >> setpagedevice"
*End
*MediaType THICK/Thick: "<</MediaType (Thick)
 /Policies <</MediaType 2>> >> setpagedevice"
*End
*MediaType TABSTOCK/Tab Stock: "<</MediaType (Tabstock)
 /Policies <</MediaType 2>> >> setpagedevice"
*End
*MediaType TRANSPR/Transparency: "<</MediaType (Transparency)
 /Policies <</MediaType 2>> >> setpagedevice"
*End
*MediaType TRANSLU/Translucent: "<</MediaType (Translucent)
 /Policies <</MediaType 2>> >> setpagedevice"
*End

*?MediaType: "save
 currentpagedevice /MediaType 2 copy known
 {get
[[(None)    ()]
 [(PLAIN)   (Plain)]
 [(THICK) (Thick)]
 [(TRANSPR) (Transparency)]
 [(SPECIAL)  (Special)]
 [(RECYCLED)(Recycled)]
 [(TRANSLU)(Translucent)]
 [(TABSTOCK)   (Tabstock)]]
 {aload pop 2 index eq {(1) exit}{pop} ifelse} forall
 (1) eq {exch pop} {(Unknown)} ifelse
 } {pop pop (None)} ifelse
 = flush
restore"
*End
*CloseUI: *MediaType

